'''路坦力'''（{{lang-en|'''Nutanix'''}}），是一家設計與銷售[[超融合基礎架構|超融合基礎架構]]設備的資訊科技公司。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.watchstor.com/corp-144293.htm |title=最酷供应商Nutanix(路坦力)宣布拓展中国计划 |website=WatchStor.com |publisher=51CTO |date=2013-06-05 |access-date=2016-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150829012335/http://news.watchstor.com/corp-144293.htm |archive-date=2015-08-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>
<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.businessinsider.com.au/heres-why-billion-dollar-startup-nutanix-is-happy-to-give-away-all-its-secrets-2014-3 |title=Here's Why Billion Dollar Startup Nutanix Is Happy To Give Away All Its Secrets |publisher=Business Insider Australia |last=Pash |first=Chris |date=2014-03-04 |access-date=2016-09-11 |archive-date=2016-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160911095001/http://www.businessinsider.com.au/heres-why-billion-dollar-startup-nutanix-is-happy-to-give-away-all-its-secrets-2014-3 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
他們的產品提供了{{link-en|軟體定義式|Software-defined infrastructure
}}的資訊科技基礎架構，該架構執行[[虛擬化|虛擬化]]的應用程序並且提供了許多公共[[雲端運算|雲服務]]的優點。運算、虛擬、以及儲存的資源都被融合至一台可橫向擴展的[[x86|x86]]伺服器（站點），並將之部署在執行Nutanix Acropolis軟體的[[计算机集群|叢集]]之中。Nutanix叢集消除了對外部儲存陣列裝置的依賴——譬如[[儲存區域網路|儲存區域網路]]跟[[網路附加儲存|網路附加儲存]]。整個系統的能力可透過增加額外的站點來擴充。另外，Nutanix Prism軟體則提供了自動配置、管理及分析的功能。

Nutanix的軟體除了透過經銷商銷售之外，也有搭配自己設計的伺服器成爲一個軟硬體整合解決方案。另外，也與[[戴爾|戴爾]]及[[联想集团|聯想]]達成了代工合作協議，在他們的伺服器上銷售Nutanix軟體。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2014/06/24/dell_signs_oem_deal_with_nutanix/ |title=Dell inks OEM deal with Nutanix to build mutant server, storage, networking beasts |last=Mellor |first=Chris |date=2014-05-24 |work=The Register |accessdate=2016-09-21 |archive-date=2016-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161019004330/http://www.theregister.co.uk/2014/06/24/dell_signs_oem_deal_with_nutanix/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>但是，與戴爾的合作關係隨著戴爾收購[[EMC|EMC]]將變得複雜。<ref name="YSverdlik">{{cite web|author1=Yevgeniy Sverdlik|title=Nutanix May Become First Hyperconverged Infrastructure Startup to Go Public|url=http://www.datacenterknowledge.com/archives/2015/12/24/nutanix-may-become-first-hyperconverged-infrastructure-startup-to-go-public/|website=Data Center Knowledge|accessdate=2016-09-21|date=2015-12-24|archive-date=2016-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160912075112/http://www.datacenterknowledge.com/archives/2015/12/24/nutanix-may-become-first-hyperconverged-infrastructure-startup-to-go-public/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2016年8月, 該公司宣佈其軟體開始支持{{link-en|思科UCS伺服器|Cisco Unified Computing System}}。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.computerdealernews.com/news/nutanix-expands-third-party-support-to-cisco-ucs/49788 |website=Computer Dealer News |last=Talbot |first=Chris |date=2016-08-18 |title=Nutanix expands third-party support to Cisco UCS |access-date=2016-09-21 |archive-date=2016-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160918222507/http://www.computerdealernews.com/news/nutanix-expands-third-party-support-to-cisco-ucs/49788 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==技術==
Nutanix軟體爲虛擬機，可運行在{{link-en|VMWare vSphere|VMWare vSphere}}與微軟的[[Hyper-V|Hyper-V]]，亦或者是Nutanix内建的AHV虛擬平台（源自於[[基于内核的虚拟机|KVM]]）。執行Nutanix軟體的伺服器會被叢集在一起，並透過一臺外部的[[網路交換器|以太網交換機]]互連。Nutanix軟體透過光纖將每個站點的本地儲存硬盤全部匯聚在一起形成儲存池，然後將之提供給[[Hypervisor|虛擬機監視器]]並依其需要而模擬成[[NFS|NFS]]、[[伺服器訊息區塊|SMB3]]或[[iSCSI|iSCSI]]裝置。

==沿革==
路坦力爲德拉傑·潘迪（Dheeraj Pandey）, {{link-en|莫希特·阿倫|Mohit Aron}}（Mohit Aron）和阿吉特·辛格（Ajeet Singh）在2009年所創辦<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/brucerogers/2013/10/26/will-dheeraj-pandeys-nutanix-be-the-next-vmware-of-the-datacenter/#39fb3f4e40ce |title=Will Dheeraj Pandey's Nutanix Be the Next VMware of the Data Center? |date=2013-10-26 |publisher=Forbes |access-date=2016-08-24 |archive-date=2016-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816134529/http://www.forbes.com/sites/brucerogers/2013/10/26/will-dheeraj-pandeys-nutanix-be-the-next-vmware-of-the-datacenter/#39fb3f4e40ce |dead-url=no }}</ref>，總部在美國加州聖荷西，產品銷售遍及超過70個國家。

2013年，阿倫離開了路坦力創辦了{{tsl|en|Cohesity|凝聚力 (公司)|凝聚力}}（Cohesity），一家專門收集與管理{{lang-en|次級資料|Secondary data}}的大網路規模平臺公司。<ref name="Networkworld">{{cite web |author=Bob Brown |title=Google-infused storage startup Cohesity reveals itself |date=2015-06-17 |url=http://www.networkworld.com/article/2936660/network-storage/google-infused-storage-startup-cohesity-reveals-itself.html |publisher=Network World |accessdate=2016-09-21 |archive-date=2016-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160902053202/http://www.networkworld.com/article/2936660/network-storage/google-infused-storage-startup-cohesity-reveals-itself.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
該公司在超過5輪的募資中從風險投資公司總共獲得了3.122億美元的資金，並在2013年前市值達到10億美元而使之成爲[[独角兽_(公司)|獨角獸公司]]之一。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blogs.wsj.com/venturecapital/2014/01/14/nutanix-joins-the-1-billion-valuation-club-as-it-takes-on-tech-giants/ |website=The Wall Street Journal |last=Gage |first=Deborah |date=2014-01-14 |title=Nutanix Joins the $1 Billion Valuation Club as It Takes On Tech Giants |access-date=2016-09-21 |archive-date=2016-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161014042214/http://blogs.wsj.com/venturecapital/2014/01/14/nutanix-joins-the-1-billion-valuation-club-as-it-takes-on-tech-giants/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2014年該公司在E回合募資籌得1.4億美元資金而使得市值達到了20億美元左右。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://techcrunch.com/2014/08/27/nutanix-lands-140m-on-2b-valuation-to-keep-growing-converged-infrastructure/ |title=Nutanix Lands $140M On $2B+ Valuation, IPO Could Be Next |last=Miller |first=Ron |date=2014-08-27 |website=TechCrunch |accessdate=2016-09-21 |archive-date=2016-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160927100503/https://techcrunch.com/2014/08/27/nutanix-lands-140m-on-2b-valuation-to-keep-growing-converged-infrastructure/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2015年12月，路坦力公司申請[[首次公开募股|首次公開發行]]，並披露2015年7月底止的前一財年淨虧損1.26億美元。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://edgar.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1618732/000119312515411021/d937439ds1.htm |title=Form S-1 Registration Statement |date=2015-12-22 |publisher=US Securities and Exchange Commission |accessdate=2016-09-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914224307/http://edgar.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1618732/000119312515411021/d937439ds1.htm |archivedate=2016-09-14 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/petercohan/2015/12/29/will-nutanix-kill-2016s-tech-ipo-market |title=Will Nutanix Kill 2016's Tech IPO Market? |date=2016-08-26 |publisher=Forbes |author=Peter Cohan |accessdate=2016-09-21 |archive-date=2016-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020160414/http://www.forbes.com/sites/petercohan/2015/12/29/will-nutanix-kill-2016s-tech-ipo-market/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>發行說明書公開後經過多次更新，包括在2016年8月16日的版本，報告了收入及虧損均持續增長，以及正向的營運現金流。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://edgar.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1618732/000119312516683250/d937439ds1a.htm |title=Ammendment to Form S-1 Registration Statement |date=2016-08-16 |publisher=US Securities and Exchange Commission |accessdate=2016-09-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914233347/http://edgar.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1618732/000119312516683250/d937439ds1a.htm |archivedate=2016-09-14 }}</ref> 2016年8月下旬，路坦力公司公告已經併購了PernixData及Calm.io兩家公司。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nutanix.com/2016/08/29/shared-ambition/ |title=Shared Ambitio n |date=2016-08-29 |author=Sunil Potti |website=Nutanix Blog |accessdate=2016-09-21 |archive-date=2016-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160911052442/http://www.nutanix.com/2016/08/29/shared-ambition/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bizjournals.com/sanjose/blog/techflash/2016/08/nutanix-scoops-pair-of-companies.html |title=Nutanix scoops up pair of companies |date=2016-08-28 |work=Silicon Valley Business Journal |author=Cromwell Shubarth |accessdate=2016-09-21 |archive-date=2016-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160911185014/http://www.bizjournals.com/sanjose/blog/techflash/2016/08/nutanix-scoops-pair-of-companies.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>根據報導，Calm.io的業務爲雲自動化及[[编配_(计算机)|編排]]服務，其背後有[[紅杉資本|紅杉資本]]的資金。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://calm.io/about-us/ |title=About Us |publisher=calm.io |archivedate=2016-03-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320094137/https://calm.io/about-us/ |accessdate=2016-09-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>路坦力有可能成爲第一家公開上市的超融合基礎架構新創企業<ref name="YSverdlik"></ref>，不過也有分析師認爲路坦力上市日期將會延緩。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.thestreet.com/story/13689512/1/cnbc-s-pisani-forecasts-possible-fall-ipos.html |website=The Street |last=Bruno |first=Giovanni |date=2016-08-30 |title=CNBC's Pisani Forecasts Possible Fall IPOs |accessdate=2016-09-21 |archive-date=2016-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919065754/https://www.thestreet.com/story/13689512/1/cnbc-s-pisani-forecasts-possible-fall-ipos.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2018 年 3 月，Nutanix 宣布收購位於班加羅爾的 Minjar。同年晚些時候，Nutanix 收購了 DaaS 初創公司 Frame<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.mg21.com/ntnx.html |title=企业级云计算公司：路坦力Nutanix, Inc.(NTNX) |publisher=美股之家 |date=2021-06-06 |access-date=2021-06-11 |archive-date=2020-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919130852/https://www.mg21.com/ntnx.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

